            <h4>To pass a degree you need to complete all compulsory courses, at least 3 courses from the directive courses which you can use to fill in major and elective spaces.</h4>
            <p>
                Tip: Each subject is worth 10 units!
            </p>
        <img src="Images/uniclass2.png" /> 
